## 📊 Dataset Description

The project uses a simulated multi-class news dataset containing articles from four categories:

* Business
* Technology
* Sports
* Health

Each record consists of:

* News headline/text
* Category label

Example:

| Text                               | Category   |
| ---------------------------------- | ---------- |
| Stock markets rally after earnings | Business   |
| New AI software released           | Technology |
| Football team wins match           | Sports     |
| Doctors warn about health risks    | Health     |

The dataset represents realistic news classification scenarios.

